
// The code sends a SignalR message to users with the "root" role using the [sockets.signal] slot. It specifies the method "magic.workflows.action" and includes arguments in JSON format, with a "type" set to "error" and a "message" retrieved from the [.arguments] node.
sockets.signal:magic.workflows.action
   roles:root
   args
      type:error
      message:x:@.arguments/*/message
